{"segment_id": "mozi-011-identification-with-the-superior-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0001", "section_id": "mozi-011-identification-with-the-superior-i", "source_id": "mozi-011-identification-with-the-superior-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 1, "text_original": "子墨子言曰：", "text_normalized": "子墨子言曰：", "canonical_ref": "11.1", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-011-identification-with-the-superior-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0002", "section_id": "mozi-011-identification-with-the-superior-i", "source_id": "mozi-011-identification-with-the-superior-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 2, "text_original": "古者民始生、未有刑政之時，蓋其語，人異義。", "text_normalized": "古者民始生、未有刑政之時，蓋其語，人異義。", "canonical_ref": "11.2", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-011-identification-with-the-superior-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0003", "section_id": "mozi-011-identification-with-the-superior-i", "source_id": "mozi-011-identification-with-the-superior-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 3, "text_original": "是以一人則一義，二人則二義，十人則十義。", "text_normalized": "是以一人則一義，二人則二義，十人則十義。", "canonical_ref": "11.3", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-011-identification-with-the-superior-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0004", "section_id": "mozi-011-identification-with-the-superior-i", "source_id": "mozi-011-identification-with-the-superior-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 4, "text_original": "其人茲衆，其所謂義者亦茲衆。", "text_normalized": "其人茲衆，其所謂義者亦茲衆。", "canonical_ref": "11.4", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-011-identification-with-the-superior-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0005", "section_id": "mozi-011-identification-with-the-superior-i", "source_id": "mozi-011-identification-with-the-superior-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 5, "text_original": "是以人是其義，以非人之義，故交相非也。", "text_normalized": "是以人是其義，以非人之義，故交相非也。", "canonical_ref": "11.5", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-011-identification-with-the-superior-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0006", "section_id": "mozi-011-identification-with-the-superior-i", "source_id": "mozi-011-identification-with-the-superior-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 6, "text_original": "是以內者父子、兄弟作怨惡，離散不能相和合。", "text_normalized": "是以內者父子、兄弟作怨惡，離散不能相和合。", "canonical_ref": "11.6", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-011-identification-with-the-superior-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0007", "section_id": "mozi-011-identification-with-the-superior-i", "source_id": "mozi-011-identification-with-the-superior-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 7, "text_original": "天下之百姓，皆以水火、毒藥相虧害。", "text_normalized": "天下之百姓，皆以水火、毒藥相虧害。", "canonical_ref": "11.7", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-011-identification-with-the-superior-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0008", "section_id": "mozi-011-identification-with-the-superior-i", "source_id": "mozi-011-identification-with-the-superior-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 8, "text_original": "至有餘力，不能以相勞。", "text_normalized": "至有餘力，不能以相勞。", "canonical_ref": "11.8", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-011-identification-with-the-superior-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0009", "section_id": "mozi-011-identification-with-the-superior-i", "source_id": "mozi-011-identification-with-the-superior-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 9, "text_original": "腐朽餘財，不以相分。", "text_normalized": "腐朽餘財，不以相分。", "canonical_ref": "11.9", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-011-identification-with-the-superior-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0010", "section_id": "mozi-011-identification-with-the-superior-i", "source_id": "mozi-011-identification-with-the-superior-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 10, "text_original": "隱匿良道，不以相教。", "text_normalized": "隱匿良道，不以相教。", "canonical_ref": "11.10", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-011-identification-with-the-superior-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0011", "section_id": "mozi-011-identification-with-the-superior-i", "source_id": "mozi-011-identification-with-the-superior-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 11, "text_original": "天下之亂，若禽獸然。", "text_normalized": "天下之亂，若禽獸然。", "canonical_ref": "11.11", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-011-identification-with-the-superior-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0012", "section_id": "mozi-011-identification-with-the-superior-i", "source_id": "mozi-011-identification-with-the-superior-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 12, "text_original": "夫明虖天下之所以亂者，生於無政長，是故選天下之賢可者，立以爲天子。", "text_normalized": "夫明虖天下之所以亂者，生於無政長，是故選天下之賢可者，立以爲天子。", "canonical_ref": "11.12", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-011-identification-with-the-superior-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0013", "section_id": "mozi-011-identification-with-the-superior-i", "source_id": "mozi-011-identification-with-the-superior-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 13, "text_original": "天子立，以其力爲未足，又選擇天下之賢可者，置立之以爲三公。", "text_normalized": "天子立，以其力爲未足，又選擇天下之賢可者，置立之以爲三公。", "canonical_ref": "11.13", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-011-identification-with-the-superior-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0014", "section_id": "mozi-011-identification-with-the-superior-i", "source_id": "mozi-011-identification-with-the-superior-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 14, "text_original": "天子、三公旣以立，以天下爲博大，遠國異土之民、是非利害之辯，不可一二而明知，故畫分萬國，立諸侯國君。", "text_normalized": "天子、三公旣以立，以天下爲博大，遠國異土之民、是非利害之辯，不可一二而明知，故畫分萬國，立諸侯國君。", "canonical_ref": "11.14", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-011-identification-with-the-superior-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0015", "section_id": "mozi-011-identification-with-the-superior-i", "source_id": "mozi-011-identification-with-the-superior-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 15, "text_original": "諸侯國君旣已立，以其力爲未足，又選擇其國之賢可者，置立之以爲正長。", "text_normalized": "諸侯國君旣已立，以其力爲未足，又選擇其國之賢可者，置立之以爲正長。", "canonical_ref": "11.15", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-011-identification-with-the-superior-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0016", "section_id": "mozi-011-identification-with-the-superior-i", "source_id": "mozi-011-identification-with-the-superior-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 16, "text_original": "正長旣已具，天子發政於天下之百姓，言曰：", "text_normalized": "正長旣已具，天子發政於天下之百姓，言曰：", "canonical_ref": "11.16", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-011-identification-with-the-superior-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0017", "section_id": "mozi-011-identification-with-the-superior-i", "source_id": "mozi-011-identification-with-the-superior-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 17, "text_original": "「聞善而不善，皆以告其上。", "text_normalized": "「聞善而不善，皆以告其上。", "canonical_ref": "11.17", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-011-identification-with-the-superior-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0018", "section_id": "mozi-011-identification-with-the-superior-i", "source_id": "mozi-011-identification-with-the-superior-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 18, "text_original": "上之所是，必皆是之。", "text_normalized": "上之所是，必皆是之。", "canonical_ref": "11.18", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-011-identification-with-the-superior-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0019", "section_id": "mozi-011-identification-with-the-superior-i", "source_id": "mozi-011-identification-with-the-superior-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 19, "text_original": "所非，必皆非之。", "text_normalized": "所非，必皆非之。", "canonical_ref": "11.19", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-011-identification-with-the-superior-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0020", "section_id": "mozi-011-identification-with-the-superior-i", "source_id": "mozi-011-identification-with-the-superior-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 20, "text_original": "上有過，則規諫之。", "text_normalized": "上有過，則規諫之。", "canonical_ref": "11.20", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-011-identification-with-the-superior-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0021", "section_id": "mozi-011-identification-with-the-superior-i", "source_id": "mozi-011-identification-with-the-superior-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 21, "text_original": "下有善，則傍薦之。", "text_normalized": "下有善，則傍薦之。", "canonical_ref": "11.21", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-011-identification-with-the-superior-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0022", "section_id": "mozi-011-identification-with-the-superior-i", "source_id": "mozi-011-identification-with-the-superior-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 22, "text_original": "上同而不下比者，此上之所賞，而下之所譽也。", "text_normalized": "上同而不下比者，此上之所賞，而下之所譽也。", "canonical_ref": "11.22", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-011-identification-with-the-superior-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0023", "section_id": "mozi-011-identification-with-the-superior-i", "source_id": "mozi-011-identification-with-the-superior-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 23, "text_original": "意若聞善而不善，不以告其上。", "text_normalized": "意若聞善而不善，不以告其上。", "canonical_ref": "11.23", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-011-identification-with-the-superior-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0024", "section_id": "mozi-011-identification-with-the-superior-i", "source_id": "mozi-011-identification-with-the-superior-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 24, "text_original": "上之所是弗能是，上之所非弗能非。", "text_normalized": "上之所是弗能是，上之所非弗能非。", "canonical_ref": "11.24", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-011-identification-with-the-superior-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0025", "section_id": "mozi-011-identification-with-the-superior-i", "source_id": "mozi-011-identification-with-the-superior-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 25, "text_original": "上有過弗規諫，下有善弗傍薦。", "text_normalized": "上有過弗規諫，下有善弗傍薦。", "canonical_ref": "11.25", "notes": ""}
